attributeList.name: train
attributeList.doc: Training sets. These are provided as a dictionary with form ``train[dimension]['labels' or 'inputs'][index]`` and contain 11552 labeled vectors for each number of dimensions between 2 and 20.

attributeList.name: test
attributeList.doc: Test sets. These are provided as a dictionary with form ``test[dimension]['labels' or 'inputs'][index]`` and contain 1902 labeled vectors for each number of dimensions between 2 and 20.
